---
title: Administración
---
flowchart TD
  S([Inicio]) --> DASH[Dashboard]
  DASH -->|Solo Administrador| ADMIN[Administración]
  ADMIN --> PER_LIST[Listado de personal]
  PER_LIST --> PER_NEW[Registrar personal]
  PER_NEW -->|Guardar| PER_LIST
  PER_LIST --> PER_DETAIL[Detalle de personal]
  PER_DETAIL --> PER_EDIT[Editar]
  PER_EDIT -->|Guardar| PER_DETAIL
  PER_DETAIL --> PER_DEACT[Desactivar]
  PER_DEACT -->|Confirmar| PER_LIST
  ADMIN --> SYSCONFIG[Configuración del sistema]